Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:01.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,電気や水道が結構残っていても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり人はいないね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,家はこんなにあるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっとたくさんの人が住んでたんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たくさんってどのくらい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:21.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,1000人とか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,多いな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっと多いかも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく分かんないな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:34.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,家ってなんのためにあるんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃ家がなかったら　暮らしていけないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今の私たちには家ないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　あれは？家じゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちの車両
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,家ではないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,「はい」か「いいえ」で答えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,家だけに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:23.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:29.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　私たちにも昔はあったけどね　家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもなくなっちゃったからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この部屋　ちゃんと扉がある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほんとだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:06.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,物がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,結構きれいな部屋だね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水も出るな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい感じの椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい眺めだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:37.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だいぶ日も落ちてきたし　いっそのこと　もうここに住みたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　住んでみる？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかすごく憧れるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,憧れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こういう所に住むの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:57.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいよね　ちゃんと天井があって　四方壁に囲まれててさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだねー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,住むんならあれが欲しいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほらベッドとか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ベッドか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人用の二段になったやつを前に見たな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:11.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おぉ　いいね　それ欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.83,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの辺に置きたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:25.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私　上上　ちーちゃんは下でいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,高いところ嫌だもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私あれも欲しいな　本棚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何って　本の入った棚だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:40.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たくさん本が入っていて…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:47.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はいはい　だったら私は食料棚が欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べ物のいっぱい詰まった棚だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あとは　暖房は欲しいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ストーブとか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それにお風呂も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:09.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人は植物とか飾ったらしいよ　やってみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ石像も飾ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,石像はいらんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいよねー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だったら最高なんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:11.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな所でもちもちしてたら　あっという間に食料が尽きちゃうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:13.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう遅いし　今日はここに泊まろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:18.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:32.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,結局　補給して移動しての繰り返しか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,つまり　この旅路が私たちの家ってわけだね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,屋根のない素敵な家だなー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いえーい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　こいつにも屋根付ける？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやいらん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　壁壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ダメだ　眠すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,休憩しよう　休憩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昨日遅かったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,明るいからつい…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやぁ　昨日は盛り上がったね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,盛り上がったというか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい　次ちーちゃんね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　今風で…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,風が吹いたかもねー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これで私が10勝だっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　もっぺんやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　明日の食料を１本賭けるってのはどう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも負けるから賭けないかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,１本？いいけど　風禁止な
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,風吹いてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:29.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,結局　ユーに１本渡すことになったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう寝てるし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でかいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,バカ　動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいか　ユー　揺れると危ないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:50.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで踊ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,てめぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいか　よく聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,揺れないようにそーっと私を…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ウケる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おまえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,覚えてろよー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここは海ってやつなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お爺さんにも見せたかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この魚…もしかしてあの時の…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　それは違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユ…ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でかいな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちなみに　あの時の魚はこいつだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べたもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚　おいしかったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も魚だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんもおいしそう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,理性はないのか　理性は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だって　魚だし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:16.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんだって　どうせ食べられるなら私がいいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それはそうかもしれないが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.83,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　ちょっと　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.83,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　待てって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめろー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べられる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,も…もう食べられない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,変な場所をいろいろ巡った気分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水おいしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:54.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:55.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨だー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はしゃいでる場合か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,屋根のある場所で降ってくれればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨宿りできる所…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,荷物にシートかけといて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あーい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,結構濡れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おっと　いい棒発見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,久しぶりだね　雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:05.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい音だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,暇だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お　いい音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく響くなー　なんでだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カンカンうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たぶん中空構造だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,中空？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,中が空っぽってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユーの頭のように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空っぽだとよく響くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてっ　いてっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:09.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おお　いい音　中が空っぽなのかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前よりは中身あるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,暇なら水でも汲んできてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　すぐ叩くんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おっ　ここがいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっとヘルメット貸して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:25.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいけど　何に使うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい音かも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっと増やしてみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨漏りはいっぱいあるしね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これとか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,見てー　缶がいっぱいあったよー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで音の洪水だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:36.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしかすると　これは音楽ってやつかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音楽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:45.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音の高低とリズムがあって　それが連なるものらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっとやりすぎたかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,かもな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:55.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨が…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:09.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつもの世界ってこんなに…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:10.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:25.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう少し休んでいこうか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:27.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.57,0:02:01.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好多電線和水管
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可就是不見一個人影
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,明明房子有這麼多
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前肯定有很多人住在這裡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,很多是多少？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.73,0:02:21.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一千個人？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可能還不止
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不太清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.44,0:02:34.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳說家是派什麼用場的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒有家的話 哪裡能生活下去啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們現在可就沒有家啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那個呢 不算家嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們的車
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不算吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,用「是」和「不是」來回答
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(957,933)}家
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳說家了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.29,0:03:23.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.96,0:03:29.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,其實 我們以前也是有過家的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是現在沒了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這個房間居然有門
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.88,0:04:06.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,裡面有東西
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這房間好整潔啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,還有水
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這椅子不錯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,風景真好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.88,0:04:37.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,太陽也快下山了 要不我們就在這裡住下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那就住住看？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我可是憧憬很久了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,憧憬？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,憧憬能住在這樣的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.84,0:04:57.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這種感覺真好 頭上有天花板 四周都是牆壁
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,既然要住在這 好想添點東西啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比如說添個床
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,床嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我之前有看到給兩人睡的上下鋪
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.26,0:05:11.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,像這樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不錯 好想要一張
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.83,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,放在那邊挺合適的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.45,0:05:25.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我要睡上鋪 小千妳就睡下面吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,反正妳也不喜歡高的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我還想要個書櫃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這還問 當然是放書的櫃子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.01,0:05:40.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能放很多書
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.12,0:05:47.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那個 那我想要一個食品櫃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,堆滿食物的櫃子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,然後 我還想要個取暖設備
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比如暖爐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,最後浴缸也不能少
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.03,0:06:09.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聽說以前的人會在房間裡裝點植物 我也想試一試
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那順便再放幾個石像吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,石像就算了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真幸福啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要是都實現了那就太棒了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.06,0:07:11.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們不能在這裡享受人生 否則很快就要沒糧食吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.94,0:07:13.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,天已經很黑了 今天就在這裡過夜吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.20,0:07:18.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.34,0:07:32.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到頭來 還是補給完就繼續上路啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也就是說 這趟旅途就是我們的家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一個沒有屋簷的家 真棒啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(957,933)}耶
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要不我們給車加個屋頂？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 要撞牆了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不行 睏死了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧 休息…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,都怪昨天睡太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,燈那麼亮 不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,昨晚玩得那叫一個開心呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那能叫開心嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 輪到妳了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 妳吹了氣吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是颳風了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 我就十連勝了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 再來一局
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要不 我們賭一份明天的乾糧吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不過肯定我贏 妳怕是不敢賭吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一份？可以 不過不准吹氣
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我可沒吹氣
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.45,0:10:29.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,結果我還是輸給了妳一份吃的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這就睡著了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼那麼大
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,傻瓜 別動
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聽好了小尤 再晃的話會很危險
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.03,0:11:50.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼開始跳舞了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳這混蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳照著我說的做
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,別晃來晃去 輕輕地把我…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好好笑
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,給我記好了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這裡就是大海嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真想讓爺爺也來看看
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這條魚…該不會就是那時的魚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不 不是的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小…小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,順便說下 這才是那時的魚
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,畢竟已經被吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,魚好好吃啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳也是條魚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千妳看起來也好好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳已經失去理智了嗎 嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳還指望魚理智？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.74,0:14:16.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,反正妳遲早會被吃掉 不如現在就讓我吃了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.83,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.83,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 讓妳等一下啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,已…已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感覺逛了好多奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,水真好喝
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.00,0:15:54.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.23,0:15:55.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,下雨啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,別調皮了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼偏偏挑我們在外面趕路的時候下
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,得找能避雨的地方…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,用防水布把行李蓋起來
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,濕透了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,找到根能用的棒子
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好久沒下雨了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.89,0:17:05.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聲音好響
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好無聊啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聲音好好聽
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,居然有迴響 為什麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,別敲 吵死了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這裡有可能是中空結構
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,中空？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是裡面是空的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就像妳的腦袋瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,空心的話就容易產生迴響
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原來如…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.44,0:18:05.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.32,0:18:09.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聲音真好聽 妳的腦袋瓜也是空的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再空也空不過妳
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒事幹的話就去接點水來
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的是 有事沒事就來打我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就這裡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,頭盔借我用下
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.85,0:19:25.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可以是可以 但妳要用來幹什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,聲音真好聽
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再多擺點東西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,畢竟到處都在漏雨
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比如這個
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看 我找到了好多空罐子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就像聲音的洪水一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.51,0:20:36.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我在想 這或許是就是所謂的音樂
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,音樂？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.52,0:20:45.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,把高低不齊的聲音和節奏串起來 似乎就會形成音樂
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是不是擺太多了？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.32,0:20:55.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,雨停了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我說 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.56,0:23:09.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,平常的世界原來…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.64,0:23:10.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.32,0:23:25.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們再休息一會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.44,0:23:27.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是
